title: Simulated Time Series and their ACF and PACF
format: html
engine: knitr

---

Using `webr` to showcase simulated arima processes, written in the form ARIMA(p, d, q).

```{webr-r}
ts.sim <- arima.sim(list(order = c(1,1,0), ar = 0.7), n = 200)
ts.plot(ts.sim)
acf(ts.sim)
pacf(ts.sim)
```
